    "content": "<p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Knowing what your business is worth is not just an academic exercise — it drives real decisions around fundraising, partnership buyouts, succession planning, and exit strategies. <strong className=\"text-black\">Business valuation</strong> provides an objective, defensible estimate of your company&apos;s economic value based on its financial performance, market position, and growth potential.</p><p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">At Majed Alshamsi Auditing, our <strong className=\"text-black\">business valuation</strong> experts apply multiple methodologies — discounted cash flow analysis, comparable company analysis, and precedent transaction methods — to arrive at a fair and well-supported figure. Every engagement is led by experienced professionals who understand the nuances of UAE market conditions.</p><p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Whether you&apos;re preparing for an investor pitch, settling a shareholder dispute, or planning a strategic acquisition, a credible business valuation gives you the numbers you need to negotiate from strength. We&apos;ve valued companies across sectors including technology, hospitality, real estate, healthcare, and professional services in the UAE.</p><h3 className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-thm mb-5\">Our Business Valuation Services Include:</h3><ul className=\"flex flex-col gap-3 text-lg list-disc ml-8 mb-10\"><li>Full Enterprise Valuation (DCF, Market, Asset-Based Approaches)</li><li>Equity &amp; Shareholder Value Assessments</li><li>Valuation for Mergers &amp; Acquisitions</li><li>Goodwill &amp; Intangible Asset Valuation</li><li>Purchase Price Allocation (PPA)</li><li>Fairness Opinions &amp; Independent Expert Reports</li></ul><p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">A thorough business valuation is an investment in clarity. Reach out to our team to get started with a confidential assessment of your company&apos;s value.</p>"
