    "featuredImage": "/img/service/main/corporate-tax.webp",
    "content": "<p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">The introduction of <strong className=\"text-black\">corporate tax</strong> in the UAE has fundamentally changed how businesses plan their finances. With a 9% tax rate on profits exceeding AED 375,000, companies need to ensure their tax structures, documentation, and filing processes are airtight from day one. Majed Alshamsi Auditing provides comprehensive corporate tax services that cover every aspect of compliance.</p><p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Our <strong className=\"text-black\">corporate tax</strong> team works with businesses of all sizes — from free zone entities to mainland operations and multinational groups with complex intercompany structures. We handle the entire lifecycle: registration with the Federal Tax Authority, calculation of taxable income, preparation of returns, and ongoing advisory to optimize your tax position within the law.</p><p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Getting corporate tax wrong can be expensive. Penalties for late registration, missed filing deadlines, and incorrect calculations add up quickly. Our professionals stay on top of every FTA update and ministerial decision to ensure your business remains fully compliant.</p><h3 className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-thm mb-5\">Our Corporate Tax Services Include:</h3><ul className=\"flex flex-col gap-3 text-lg list-disc ml-8 mb-10\"><li>Corporate Tax Registration &amp; TRN Obtainment</li><li>Taxable Income Computation</li><li>Tax Return Preparation &amp; Filing</li><li>Free Zone Qualifying Income Assessment</li><li>Transfer Pricing Documentation</li><li>Corporate Tax Planning &amp; Advisory</li></ul><p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Don&apos;t navigate the UAE&apos;s corporate tax landscape alone. Our team has the expertise to keep your business compliant and your tax liability optimized. Reach out for a consultation.</p>"
