    "headline": "Corporate Tax Filing",
    "featuredImage": "/img/service/corporate-tax/corporate-tax-filing.webp",
    "content": "<p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Timely and accurate <strong className=\"text-black\">corporate tax filing</strong> is not optional — it&apos;s a legal requirement under the UAE Corporate Tax Law. Every taxable business must submit its returns to the Federal Tax Authority by the prescribed deadlines or face financial penalties. Majed Alshamsi Auditing takes the burden off your plate by handling the entire filing process from calculation to submission.</p><p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Our <strong className=\"text-black\">corporate tax filing</strong> service begins with a thorough review of your financial records to compute taxable income accurately. We identify all applicable deductions, exemptions, and reliefs — including small business relief and free zone benefits — to ensure you never pay more than you legally owe.</p><p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Mistakes in corporate tax filing can trigger audits, reassessments, and penalties. Our team cross-checks every figure against FTA guidelines and supporting documentation before submission. After filing, we maintain complete records and handle any follow-up correspondence from the tax authorities on your behalf.</p><h3 className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-thm mb-5\">Our Corporate Tax Filing Services Include:</h3><ul className=\"flex flex-col gap-3 text-lg list-disc ml-8 mb-10\"><li>Taxable Income Computation &amp; Adjustments</li><li>Tax Return Preparation &amp; Review</li><li>Deduction &amp; Exemption Optimization</li><li>Electronic Submission to FTA</li><li>Deadline Monitoring &amp; Calendar Management</li><li>Post-Filing Support &amp; FTA Query Response</li></ul><p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Let the experienced team at MAJED ALSHAMSI AUDITING handle your corporate tax filing so you can focus on growing your business with confidence.</p>"
