    "headline": "Risk Advisory",
    "featuredImage": "/img/service/main/risk-advisory.jpeg",
    "content": "<p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Every business faces risks — market volatility, regulatory changes, operational disruptions, and cybersecurity threats, to name a few. The question isn&apos;t whether risks exist, but whether you&apos;ve identified them and put measures in place to manage them. <strong className=\"text-black\">Risk advisory</strong> at Majed Alshamsi Auditing helps businesses across Dubai build resilience by systematically identifying, assessing, and mitigating the threats that could impact their objectives.</p><p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Our <strong className=\"text-black\">risk advisory</strong> professionals work across industries — from construction and trading to financial services and healthcare — to deliver practical risk management frameworks that your leadership team can actually use. We don&apos;t produce theoretical documents that sit in a drawer; we build risk registers, heat maps, and action plans that inform daily decision-making.</p><p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Whether you need a comprehensive enterprise risk assessment, a targeted review of a specific function, or ongoing risk advisory support, our team tailors each engagement to your organization&apos;s size, complexity, and appetite for risk. We also help you communicate risk positions to boards, investors, and regulators with clarity and confidence.</p><h3 className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-thm mb-5\">Our Risk Advisory Services Include:</h3><ul className=\"flex flex-col gap-3 text-lg list-disc ml-8 mb-10\"><li>Enterprise Risk Management (ERM) Framework Design</li><li>Risk Identification, Assessment &amp; Prioritization</li><li>Internal Controls &amp; Compliance Risk Review</li><li>Business Continuity &amp; Disaster Recovery Planning</li><li>Fraud Risk Assessment &amp; Prevention</li><li>Board-Level Risk Reporting &amp; Governance Advisory</li></ul><p className=\"text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Proactive risk advisory protects your business before problems escalate. Contact our team to schedule a risk assessment of your organization.</p>"
